"38:10:3" : {s: 38, a: 10, w: 3, r: "ملك", t: "مُّلْكُ", l: "مُلْك", lc: 48, tl: "mul'ku", lb: "সার্বভৌমত্ব, রাজত্ব ও কর্তৃত্ব, আধিপত্য, সাম্রাজ্য, ক্ষমতা",e: "(is the) dominion", b: "কর্তৃত্ব, রাজত্ব", i: "kerajaan", f: 1, rm: "to rule/command/reign, be capable, to control, power/authority, king, kingdom."},
"38:10:4" : {s: 38, a: 10, w: 4, r: "سمو", t: "ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ", l: "سَمَآء", lc: 310, tl: "l-samāwāti", lb: "আকাশ, মহাকাশ, আমাদের উপরে সব কিছু",e: "(of) the heavens", b: "আসমান সমূহের", i: "langit", f: 175, rm: ""},
"38:10:5" : {s: 38, a: 10, w: 5, r: "ارض", t: "وَٱلْأَرْضِ", l: "أَرْض", lc: 461, tl: "wal-arḍi", lb: "পৃথিবী",e: "and the earth", b: "এবং যমীনের", i: "dan bumi", f: 108, rm: "To rotate, bring forth herbs abundantly. Land abundant, fruitful, productive, luxuriant with herbage. Place for alighting or abiding. To tarry, await, expect, be patient. Earth, as opposed to heaven: and the ground, as meaning the surface of the earth, on which we tread, and sit, and lie. Good land. Remain, fixed, tarry in expectation [on the ground]. Heavy, slow, sluggish, inclining, or propending to the ground. Submissive. A carpet, anything that is spread. A tremor, vertigo arising from a relaxed state. Wood-fretter, termite."},
"38:10:6" : {s: 38, a: 10, w: 6, r: "", t: "وَمَا", l: "مَا", lc: 2557, tl: "wama", lb: "না, যা, কী/কীসে?",e: "and whatever", b: "এবং যা", i: "dan apa", f: 646, rm: ""},
"38:10:7" : {s: 38, a: 10, w: 7, r: "بين", t: "بَيْنَهُمَا", l: "بَيْن", lc: 266, tl: "baynahumā", lb: "মধ্যে",e: "(is) between them", b: "তাদের মাঝে", i: "diantara keduanya", f: 29, rm: ""},
"38:10:8" : {s: 38, a: 10, w: 8, r: "رقي", t: "فَلْيَرْتَقُوا۟", l: "يَرْتَقُ", lc: 1, tl: "falyartaqū", lb: "",e: "Then let them ascend", b: "তারা যেন আরোহণ করে", i: "maka hendaklah mereka menaiki", f: 1, rm: "to ascend, rise gradually, mount a ladder. mirqat - stair, ladder, stepping-stone, ascent. raqin - physician, charmer. taraqiya (pl. of tarquwutun) - collar bone(s), throat, clavicle (according to some its root is raqawa or tarqawa)."},
"38:10:9" : {s: 38, a: 10, w: 9, r: "", t: "فِى", l: "فِى", lc: 1675, tl: "fee", lb: "ভেতরে, মধ্যে",e: "by", b: "মধ্যে", i: "pada", f: 1184, rm: ""},
